title: Sinbad Interview and More
itunes:title: Sinbad Interview and More
description:
Thursday 3/1 - Today on the show we had comedian/ actor Sinbad stop by and spoke about Monique, being mad at Justin Timberlake Superbowl performance and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Wesley Jamar Johnson from the Clippers after his embarrassing fall during the Clippers vs. Rockets NBA game last night, and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
